  <description type="morphology">Plants 8–40 cm. Stems tomentose, sometimes stipitate-glandular distally. Leaves 5–20 × 2–3.5 cm, pinnately lobed (lobes dentate; distal cauline stipitate-glandular and with large dark or black setae). Heads 15–30. Peduncles stipitate-glandular. Phyllaries 7–8, stipitate-glandular and with dark or black, glandular setae. Florets 10–14. Cypselae golden brown. 2n = 44.</description>
